---
title: Sticky Honey Beef Rice Bowl with Green Beans
description: This Sticky Honey Beef Rice Bowl is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R02_W15_UK_G12279-15912-8_Main_low-11b8b467.jpg
